content.rendered:
Buy Gift Card via Credit Card 
Buy Gift Card via Paypal

Gift Card

Give the gift of relaxation and beauty with a York Street Spa gift card. Perfect for any occasion, our gift cards can be used for a wide range of spa services, from rejuvenating facials and soothing massages to hairstyling and more. Treat your loved ones to a pampering experience they’ll cherish. Purchase a York Street Spa gift card today and spread the joy of self-care and relaxation.

When purchasing a York Street Spa gift card online, we offer three convenient delivery methods to suit your preferences:

  • You can choose to have the gift card mailed directly to yourself or the recipient
  • Opt to keep it securely on file at YSS for easy access
  • Visit our spa in person to pick it up.

After completing your gift card purchase, you’ll receive an email from YSS requesting “special instructions.” In this email, please provide the recipient’s first name, last name, and phone number, which will be helpful in case the card is ever misplaced. Once we receive this information, we will process your gift card according to your chosen specifications.

Please be aware that PayPal orders typically take 24-48 hours to process, excluding shipping time if you select the mailing option. It’s important to note that all gift card sales are final and non-refundable, ensuring that your gift of relaxation is a thoughtful and lasting gesture.
